Package: retroarch
Architecture: armhf
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libsdl-image1.2, libsdl-ttf2.0-0, libsdl1.2debian, libsdl-image1.2, libopenal1, libqtgui4, libsdl-ttf2.0-0
Replaces: ssnes
Description: A simple frontend for the libretro library.
 .
 RetroArch attempts to be very small and lean, while still having all of the useful
 core features expected form an emulator. It is a command-line-only interface, though RetroArch-Phoenix provides a minimal GUI.
 .
 RetroArch supports both Cg shaders and bsnes-style XML shaders.
